  "name": "RPlog_The_Trandoshan_Expedition",
  "title": "The Cave on Trandosha",
  "summary": "An Imperial reconnaissance party led by the enigmatic advisor Sinestra -- known as Ms. Starling -- crosses the volcanic, fog-choked wastes of Trandosha by hovercraft toward a target cave, accompanied by Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin and the pilot ensigns Breya Marie and Lionheart Crimson. The journey across bubbling seas of sulphuric mud strains the craft and their nerves, and a hair-raising cliff climb reveals glimpses of a strange glowing blue tattoo on Sinestra's back and a moment where Breya inexplicably defies a fatal fall -- leading the watchful Danik to suspect both women may be Force-sensitive. Inside the cave, Lionheart's blaster fire only stirs an enormous fire-breathing serpent that devours a gizka and maims his hand. Danik shields Breya and opens up with a shotgun while Sinestra drives the beast back with cryobang grenades, then -- over the objections of Danik and Breya, who want to press on out of respect for the price already paid -- orders the mission aborted. The party ropes down to their hovercraft and retreats across the cooling mud as the wounded, half-blinded creature returns to its lair and bellows after them.",
